    <div class="container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>At TaskMaster AI, we take your privacy seriously. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data when you use our services. By using TaskMaster AI, you agree to the terms outlined below.</p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect and store the following types of data:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> When you create an account, we collect personal information such as your name and email address for user authentication.</li>
            <li><strong>User-Generated Data:</strong> We collect information related to the tasks, goals, projects, and plans that you create and store in Firebase Firestore. This data may include descriptions, deadlines, statuses, and other relevant details about your tasks and projects.</li>
            <li><strong>AI-Generated Data:</strong> TaskMaster AI features, such as Smart Overview and AI notes, use the data you input to generate content. This content is processed in real-time but is not stored in Firebase Firestore unless explicitly saved as part of your notes or quizzes.</li>
            <li><strong>Friends and Messages:</strong> TaskMaster AI allows you to add friends and send messages to them. These messages are stored securely in Firebase Firestore to facilitate communication with your friends.</li>
            <li><strong>Profile Pictures:</strong> You can upload a profile picture to personalize your TaskMaster experience. These profile pictures are securely stored in Firebase Firestore and are not publicly accessible. Your profile picture is protected to ensure your privacy.</li>
            <li><strong>Calendar Events:</strong> TaskMaster AI lets you add events to your calendar. These events are stored in Firebase Firestore and help you manage your schedule.</li>
            <li><strong>AI Chat Bot:</strong> TaskMaster AI provides an in-app AI chat bot for user interactions. Messages exchanged with the AI chat bot are not stored in Firebase Firestore and are used solely for real-time interactions with the AI.</li>
            <li><strong>Notifications:</strong> TaskMaster AI may request permission to send notifications to your device. These notifications are used to alert you about important messages from your friends and updates related to your tasks, projects, and events. Notifications are not stored in Firebase Firestore.</li>
            <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> TaskMaster AI may request access to your location in order to provide weather data relevant to your location. This location data is used temporarily to provide weather updates and is not saved or stored in Firebase Firestore.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>Your data is used for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Task Management:</strong> Your data is stored in Firebase Firestore to allow you to manage tasks, goals, projects, and plans efficiently. This helps you stay organized and track progress over time.</li>
            <li><strong>AI Features:</strong> We use your data to provide AI-driven features, such as generating a Smart Overview of your tasks and generating notes and quiz questions based on your data. While the Smart Overview content is generated using your data, it is not stored in Firebase Firestore. The AI-generated notes and quiz questions may be stored in Firebase Firestore for future reference and use.</li>
            <li><strong>Friendship and Messaging:</strong> Your friend connections and messages are stored to allow you to communicate and share your progress with others in TaskMaster AI. Messages are securely stored in Firebase Firestore to facilitate these interactions.</li>
            <li><strong>Profile Customization:</strong> We store your profile picture securely in Firebase Firestore to allow you to personalize your TaskMaster AI experience. Your profile picture is protected and not publicly visible.</li>
            <li><strong>Event Management:</strong> We store your calendar events in Firebase Firestore to help you organize and track your tasks and deadlines.</li>
            <li><strong>Improvement of Services:</strong> We may use the data to improve our AI models, personalize your experience, and enhance the overall performance of TaskMaster AI.</li>
            <li><strong>Notifications:</strong> Notifications are used to keep you updated on important events, tasks, and messages, and to help you stay connected with your friends. These notifications are not stored in Firebase Firestore.</li>
            <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> Location data is used temporarily to provide weather updates and other location-based features. This data is not stored in Firebase Firestore.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Data Storage and Retention</h2>
        <p>We store your task, goal, project, and plan data in Firebase Firestore. Additionally, messages with friends, profile pictures, and calendar events are also stored in Firebase Firestore. However, the content generated by AI features, such as the Smart Overview and AI notes, is processed in real-time and not stored unless explicitly saved by the user.</p>
        <p>Notifications and location data are used only for real-time notifications and weather updates and are not saved or stored in Firebase Firestore.</p>
        <p>We retain your data as long as your account is active. You can delete your data at any time through the app. If you choose to delete your account, your data stored in Firebase Firestore will be removed in accordance with our data retention policy.</p>

        <h2>How We Protect Your Information</h2>
        <p>We take appropriate security measures to protect your personal data, including encryption and secure access controls. Your profile pictures and messages are stored securely and are protected to ensure privacy. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to protect your personal information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.</p>

        <h2>Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
        <p>We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience with TaskMaster AI. Cookies help us remember your preferences and analyze how you interact with our app. You can control cookies through your browser settings, but doing so may affect the functionality of the service.</p>

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>TaskMaster AI uses third-party services, such as Firebase Firestore and other tools for AI processing, to store and process your data. These services are used only for the purpose of providing the functionality you request and are governed by their respective privacy policies.</p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access, update, and delete your personal data at any time. If you wish to request a copy of your data or delete it, please contact us at <a href="mailto:taskmasteroneai@gmail.com">taskmasteroneai@gmail.com</a>.</p>

        <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. Please review the policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your data.</p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy or how your data is handled, please contact us at <a href="mailto:taskmasteroneai@gmail.com">taskmasteroneai@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
